==English==
===Noun===
'''hyperopia''' 

# {{pathology}} A disorder of the vision where the eye focusses images behind the [[retina]] instead of on it, so that distant objects can be seen better than near objects.

====Synonyms====
* [[farsightedness]]
* [[hypermetropia]]
* [[hypermetropy]]
* [[longsightedness]]

